dc_title_s: Map of Ann Arbor, Michigan and vicinity showing scenic boulevard and park system.
dc_description_s: Relief shown by hachures. Printed by The Ann Arbor Press. Radial distances shown. Includes key to selected buildings. 1 map: mounted on cloth; 48 x 42 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
